         "id": "SECTION_prerequisites",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nThis text is a practice based on the *Yupana Inka Tawa Pukllay* method, developed and published by Dhavit Prem (<htcite0>; <htcite1>). Therefore, we suggest that you study the previous text before proceeding (<htcite2>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "a62b520a-f443-4d83-ab51-b99c9a46dab8",
                     "text": "Prem, Dhavit",
                     "page": "pp. 354 - 363",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2018",
                        "month": "",
