      {
         "id": "SECTION_sum",
         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Exercising with the *Yupana*\n\nTo better understand the *Yupana Inka Tawa Pukllay* method, we will use a *Yupana* with 4 to perform addition. With this configuration, we can represent numbers up to **4.999**. However, it is possible to add more rows to perform sums with larger numbers without any restrictions.\n\nIn the following example, we demonstrate the addition of **512 + 513**. We invite readers to adjust the numbers and use the \"**Values**\" and \"**Result**\" options to visualize the initial numbers and the movements made during the addition. You can also modify the example values to reinforce your learning.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><input type=\"number\" value=\"512\" min=\"0\" max=\"4999\" id=\"ia2yupana0\" /> +  <input type=\"number\" value=\"513\" min=\"0\" max=\"4999\" id=\"ia2yupana1\" />:  <input type=\"radio\" value=\"values\" name=\"yupanaradio\" /> <b>Values</b> <input type=\"radio\" value=\"calcular\" name=\"yupanaradio\" /> <b>Result</b></p>",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "html",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><table id=\"yupana1\" class=\"tawapukllay\"><tr><th colspan=\"4\"><i>Yupana</i></th><th>Values</th><th>Result</th><th>Moves</th></tr> <tr id=\"tf1\"><td id=\"tc1f1\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f1\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f1\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f1\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f1\"><span id=\"vl1\"></span> + <span id=\"vr1\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f1\">&nbsp;</td><td id=\"tc7f1\" rowspan=\"5\">&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr id=\"tf2\"><td id=\"tc1f2\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f2\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f2\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f2\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f2\"><span id=\"vl2\"></span> + <span id=\"vr2\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f2\">&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr id=\"tf3\"><td id=\"tc1f3\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f3\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f3\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f3\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f3\"><span id=\"vl3\"></span> + <span id=\"vr3\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f3\">&nbsp;</td></tr> <tr id=\"tf4\"><td id=\"tc1f4\"><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_center\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c1_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_up\"></span><span class=\"dot five_dot_c2_bottom\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc2f4\"><span class=\"dot three_dot_bottom\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_up\"></span><span class=\"dot three_dot_center\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc3f4\"><span class=\"dot two_dot_bottom\"></span> <span class=\"dot two_dot_up\"></span></td> <td id=\"tc4f4\"><span class=\"dot dot_center\"></span></td><td id=\"tc5f4\"><span id=\"vl4\"></span> + <span id=\"vr4\"></span></td><td id=\"tc6f4\">&nbsp;</td></tr></table>",
